Hi Paul,

Yes, it&#39;s nice to experiment. I have to say that I find it odd to
start reading the news and immediately find the word &#39;return&#39; spelled
&#39;Roar,Eat,Tut,Roar,Nun&#39;.

It seems to me that the scale of the solution should match the scale
of the problem. I think this is a minor readability issue which will
probably go away naturally with continued reading practice, and it can
be solved quite easily with the guideline I&#39;ve just suggested of not
connecting &#39;Ado&#39; to &#39;Roar&#39; in words such as &#39;arrest&#39;.

Ted


